          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χθιζός</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χθές</span>): <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">of yesterday, yesterday</span>, usually as
          adv., <i><span class="en">Il. 1.424</span></i>.—Neut. as adv.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χθιζόν, χθιζά. χθιζά τε καὶ πρώιζα</span>,
          phrase meaning ‘but a day or two since,’ <i><span class="en">Il.
            2.303</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
